---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="daiso" channelName="daiso" channelColor="#E1261C">
<style>
.ch-header{padding:28px 0 20px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(225,38,28,.2);margin-bottom:24px}
.ch-label{font-size:9.5px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(225,38,28,.6);margin-bottom:6px}
.ch-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#E1261C;line-height:1.2}
.ch-desc{font-size:12.5px;color:#7A9AB5;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.6}
.item-card{border:1px solid rgba(225,38,28,.2);border-radius:3px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:10px;background:rgba(225,38,28,.03);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
.item-rank{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(225,38,28,.4);width:32px;flex-shrink:0;text-align:center}
.item-meta{flex:1}
.item-cat{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(225,38,28,.6);margin-bottom:4px}
.item-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:#FBF9F4;margin-bottom:3px}
.item-price{font-size:12px;color:#7A9AB5}
.cta-box{border:1px solid #5B0E1B;border-radius:3px;padding:20px 16px;margin-top:28px;text-align:center;background:rgba(91,14,27,.08)}
.cta-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:17px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}
.cta-desc{font-size:12px;color:#7A9AB5;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.6}
.cta-btn{display:block;padding:13px;background:#5B0E1B;border-radius:2px;color:#FBF9F4;font-family:'League Spartan',sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none}
</style>

<div class="ch-header">
  <div class="ch-label">taerijay+ · beauty & lifestyle</div>
  <div class="ch-title">daiso</div>
  <div class="ch-desc">다이소 뷰티 대란템 실시간 DB — 🇰🇷 매장 위치 · 재고 · 가격 정보 통합 제공</div>
</div>

<div class="item-card"><div class="item-rank">1</div><div class="item-meta"><div class="item-cat">BEAUTY · 스킨케어</div><div class="item-name">VT 리들샷 100 퍼밍 앰플</div><div class="item-price">3,000원 · 전국 전점 구비함</div></div></div>
<div class="item-card"><div class="item-rank">2</div><div class="item-meta"><div class="item-cat">BEAUTY · 마스크팩</div><div class="item-name">메디힐 TEA TREE 마스크팩 10입</div><div class="item-price">5,000원 · 온라인 대비 50% 절감함</div></div></div>
<div class="item-card"><div class="item-rank">3</div><div class="item-meta"><div class="item-cat">BEAUTY · 클렌징</div><div class="item-name">클렌징폼 · 클렌징워터 다이소 PB</div><div class="item-price">1,000~2,000원 · 가성비 1위 인증됨</div></div></div>
<div class="item-card"><div class="item-rank">4</div><div class="item-meta"><div class="item-cat">LIFESTYLE · 주방</div><div class="item-name">실리콘 주방용품 세트</div><div class="item-price">1,000~3,000원 · 인기 매진 주의 ⚠️</div></div></div>
<div class="item-card"><div class="item-rank">5</div><div class="item-meta"><div class="item-cat">STATIONERY · 문구</div><div class="item-name">다꾸 스티커 · 테이프 MD 한정판</div><div class="item-price">500~2,000원 · 시즌 한정 출시됨</div></div></div>

<div class="cta-box">
  <div class="cta-title">전체 다이소 DB 열람</div>
  <div class="cta-desc">뷰티 대란템 전체 목록 + 전국 주요 다이소 매장 위치 DB는 구독자 전용임.</div>
  <a href="/02-payment/payment?key=daiso_basic" class="cta-btn">daiso Basic 구독 — $19.99 →</a>
</div>

<script is:inline>
  if (!sessionStorage.getItem('user_email')) {
    window.location.href = '/01-auth/auth?redirect=' + encodeURIComponent(window.location.href);
  }
</script>
</Layout>